      PROGRAM vpintl
*    +            ( XIN,        XOUT,       OUTPUT,
*    +       TAPE1= XIN, TAPE2= XOUT, TAPE6=OUTPUT)
 
*     $Log: vpintl.ptn,v $
*     Revision 4.13  2014/09/25 20:20:55  dugas
